
BACnet/IP analyzer/detector for Bro
=====================================

This analyzer can parse and detect the BACnet/IP protocol as defined by
ANSI/ASHRAE 135-2016, Appendix J.


Installation
------------

Via `bro-pkg <http://bro-package-manager.readthedocs.io/en/stable/>`_::

    bro-pkg install heller/bacnet

Else you will have to build and install it yourself::

    ./configure --bro-dist=<path>
    make
    make install

